*Kathleen Ollerenshaw, Herman Bondi, &quot;Magic Squares of Order Four&quot;, Scholium Intl, 1983, 
*Kathleen Ollerenshaw, &quot;First Citizen&quot;, Hart-Davis, MacGibbon, 1977, 
